  with TiddlyWiki-rendered lists below the editor.
  Top-level lists subtract the ProseMirror editor's padding-left (28px) so that
  list text aligns with rendered <ul>/<ol> output. Nested lists (inside
  .list-content) use the full 40px indent since the parent has no extra padding. */
